  "vulnerability_information": "Hi @judgeme!\nStep to reproduce:\n1. Log in to your shopify account and create product with name `&#34;&#62;&#60;&#34;&#62;&#60;img src=x onerror=prompt(document.domain)&#62; img src=x onerror=prompt(document.domain)&#62;`\n2. Go to our store and write question to our product with name `&#34;&#62;&#60;&#34;&#62;&#60;img src=x onerror=prompt(document.domain)&#62; img src=x onerror=prompt(document.domain)&#62;`\n3. Then delete our product from store (The product status must be (out of store) in questions.\n4. Then go to Shopify admin/Judge.me Product Reviews/Questions and edit question. XSS triage\n\n\n{F1547145}\n\n\nPOC video\n\n{F1547181}\n\n## Impact\n\nsession stealer",
